              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "By author: The contribution from the beta decay of",
                "210Bi was estimated by measuring the amount of 210Po",
                "from the beta decay of 210Bi produced by neutron",
                "capture reaction in 3 grams of metallic bismuth placed",
                "at the back of the target where proton beam did not",
                "reach. This contribution was of the order of 1/300 at",
                "the maximum of the excitation function and 1/50 at Ep",
                "~ 40 MeV."
